        "body": "<p>&gt; 2H^ +8^“</p>\n<p>(v) Sulphurous acid or sulphite to sulphate or</p>\n<p>[Mn04 +8H“\" +5e“</p>\n<p>● In analytical chemistry, it is used as an oxidant in the preparation of organic compounds. ● It is used in bleaching of wool, cotton and silk, in decolourisation of oils and cleaning surgical instruments in hospitals.</p>\n<p>^2Mn^*+ IOCO2 +8H2O</p>\n<p>(iv) Hydrogen sulphide to sulphur H2S</p>\n<p>ZnO or ZnSO</p>\n<p>5Mn02 +4H'^</p>\n<p>+ 512'^ 8H2O</p>\n<p>(iii)Oxalate to carbon dioxide (at 333 K)</p>\n<p>[Mn04 +8H^ +5e</p>\n<p>+ 20H\"</p>\n<p>(iii) Manganous salt to Mn02</p>\n<p>2Mn04 +3Mn^''+2H20</p>\n<p>(ii) Ferrous salt to ferric salt</p>\n<p>Mn04 +8H'\" +5e“</p>\n<p>&gt; 8Mn02 + 680 4</p>\n<p>-&gt;Mn02+40H</p>\n<p>]x2</p>\n<p>+ 10; + 3H20+6e“</p>\n<p>&gt;IOJ +2Mn02 +20H</p>\n<p>polythene.</p>\n<p>● Iron catalyst is used in Haber’s process for the manufacture of ammonia.</p>\n<p>● Ni catalyst is used for hydrogenation of fats. ● PdCl 2 is used as a catalyst in the Wacker process (oxidation of ethyne to ethanal). ● Nickel complexes are used in the polymerisation of alkynes, benzene, etc. ● Light sensitive properties of AgBr are used in photographic industries.</p>\n<p>.</p>",
