        "body": "<p>especially, the aromatic amines due to atmospheric oxidation.</p>\n<p>Amines Physical properties of amines are as follows:</p>\n<p>● The lower aliphatic amines are gases whereas members of C3 to Cii are volatile liquids and from Ci2onwards are</p>\n<p>Physical State, Colour and Odour ● Pure amines are colourless but develop colour on keeping in air or on storage for long time.</p>\n<p>solids. ●</p>\n<p>Aromatic amines are toxic in nature.</p>\n<p>Amines</p>\n<p>Solubility</p>",
